OL,6,FThe chief executive of Royal Mail,
OL,7,FSimon Thompson, has resigned from his
OL,8,Frole after a bitter battle with its
OL,9,Fmain union which finally concluded
OL,10,Flast month.
OL,12,FMr Thompson, who has been chief
OL,13,Fexecutive of Royal Mail since 2021,
OL,14,Fsaid he believed it was "the right
OL,15,Ftime for the company to move forward
OL,16,Funder new leadership" after an
OL,17,Fagreement was struck between the
OL,18,Fcompany and union leaders last month.
